The Columbia Gas Systems Inc said redeem 4.7 mln dlrs principal amount 9-1/8 pct debenture , series due May 1 , 1996 , five mln dlrs principal amount 10-1/4 pct debenture , series due May 1 , 1999 .
The company said redeeming debenture meet mandatory sinking fund requirement .
In addition , Columbia said call optional sinking fund redemption May 1 , 1987 , 4.7 mln dlrs principal amount 9-1/8 debenture 7.5 mln dlrs 10-1/4 pct debenture .
